# Mastering Markdown Key Terms

- **Mardown** A way to control display of a document text on the web
- **SHA References** Any reference to a commitâ€™s SHA-1 hash will be automatically converted into a link to that commit on GitHub
- **Issue Reference** Any number that refers to an Issue or Pull Request will be automatically converted into a link
- **Mentions** Using @ plus a username will notify a person to go view a comment
